Question: Which hands are both ladies holding the umbrella with?

Reference Answer: left

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/4975.jpg

Original program:

```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='umbrella')
IMAGE0=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE0,object='lady')
IMAGE1=CROP(image=IMAGE0,box=BOX1)
BOX2=LOC(image=IMAGE1,object='lady')
IMAGE2=CROP(image=IMAGE1,box=BOX2)
BOX3=LOC(image=IMAGE2,object='umbrella')
ANSWER0=COUNT(box=BOX3)
ANSWER1=EVAL(expr="'both' if {ANSWER0} > 0 else 'neither'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER1)
```
